  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    The UK trade remedies investigations process
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">How the Trade Remedies Investigations Directorate will carry out transition reviews into existing EU measures and investigate if new measures are needed. </p>

  </div>
</div>

